    <content><![CDATA[<h1>Types of Training</h1><p>When considering the type of training to suit your needs, there are three main considerations: </p><ul><li>Level – Courses are offered in both Beginner (B) and Advanced (A) formats.</li><li>Topics – Courses are offered in a variety of topics: Sales and Marketing (SM), Finance (F), Logistics (L), Licenses &amp; Regulations (LR), Trade Data &amp; Analysis (TD), and Trade Problems (TP).</li><li>Geography – Courses are offered both online and in classrooms. Not all vendors are available in all states, so please refer to the chart below to determine if they have classrooms in your area.</li></ul><p>There are a number of training opportunities available to both companies who are new to exporting and companies who are experienced exporters. The chart below identifies a variety of training opportunities. These vendors may offer training in both online and classroom formats. To learn more about a specific training vendor or to view their course schedules, please follow the links below each vendor name.</p><table cellspacing="0" width="100%" class="ms-rteTable-default"><tbody><tr class="ms-rteTableHeaderRow-default"><th class="ms-rteTableHeaderFirstCol-default" rowspan="1" colspan="1" style="width:16.6667%;"><br></th><th class="ms-rteTableHeaderOddCol-default" rowspan="1" colspan="1" style="width:16.6667%;"><br></th><th class="ms-rteTableHeaderEvenCol-default" rowspan="1" colspan="1" style="width:16.6667%;"><br></th><th class="ms-rteTableHeaderOddCol-default" rowspan="1" colspan="1" style="width:16.6667%;"><br></th><th class="ms-rteTableHeaderEvenCol-default" rowspan="1" colspan="1" style="width:16.6667%;"><br></th><th class="ms-rteTableHeaderOddCol-default" rowspan="1" colspan="1" style="width:16.6667%;"><br></th></tr><tr class="ms-rteTableOddRow-default"><th class="ms-rteTableFirstCol-default" rowspan="1" colspan="1"> </th><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default"><strong>Level</strong></td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default"><strong>Topics</strong></td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default"><strong>Locations</strong></td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default"><strong>Online</strong></td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default"><strong>Classroom</strong></td></tr><tr class="ms-rteTableEvenRow-default"><th class="ms-rteTableFirstCol-default" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><strong>Online-Only Training</strong></th><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">​</td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default">​</td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">​</td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default">​</td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">​</td></tr><tr class="ms-rteTableOddRow-default"><th class="ms-rteTableFirstCol-default" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><p><strong>Bureau of Industry and Security (BIS) Online Training Room</strong></p><p><a href="http://www.bis.doc.gov/seminarsandtraining/seminar-training.htm">View Courses</a></p></th><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">B, A</td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default">LR</td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">Nationwide</td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default">X</td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default"> </td></tr><tr class="ms-rteTableEvenRow-default"><th class="ms-rteTableFirstCol-default" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><p><strong>Export-U.com</strong></p><p><a href="http://export.gov/training/eg_main_021578.asp">More Information</a></p></th><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">B</td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default">SM, F, L, LR</td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">Nationwide</td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default">X</td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default"> </td></tr><tr class="ms-rteTableOddRow-default"><th class="ms-rteTableFirstCol-default" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><p><strong>Small Business Administration</strong></p><p><a href="http://www.sba.gov/training/businessmgmt/index.html">View Courses</a></p></th><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">B</td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default"> </td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">Nationwide</td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default">X</td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default"> </td></tr><tr class="ms-rteTableEvenRow-default"><th class="ms-rteTableFirstCol-default" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><strong>Classroom Training</strong></th><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">​</td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default">​</td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">​</td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default">​</td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">​</td></tr><tr class="ms-rteTableOddRow-default"><th class="ms-rteTableFirstCol-default" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><p><strong>Census – Export Compliance Training</strong></p><p><a href="http://www.census.gov/foreign-trade/aes/meetingsandpresentations/index.html">View Schedule</a></p></th><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">B</td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default">LR</td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">Nationwide</td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default">X</td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default"> </td></tr><tr class="ms-rteTableEvenRow-default"><th class="ms-rteTableFirstCol-default" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><p><strong>Export-Import Bank of the U.S.</strong></p><p><a href="http://www.exim.gov/seminars/index.cfm">View Schedule</a></p></th><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">B</td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default">F</td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">Washington, DC</td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default"> </td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">X</td></tr><tr class="ms-rteTableOddRow-default"><th class="ms-rteTableFirstCol-default" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><p><strong>NASBITE CGBP Training</strong></p><p><a href="http://export.gov/training/eg_main_021769.asp">More Information</a><br> View Participating Programs</p></th><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">A</td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default"> </td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">Various</td><td class="ms-rteTableEvenCol-default">X</td><td class="ms-rteTableOddCol-default">X</td></tr></tbody></table><p>​</p>]]></content>
